But most chanters are 'scared' to see a tank pulling 8-20 mobs at you. <br>
Get them over that fear and you have a fun time.<br>
It seemed that it took along time to get my guild to AE, <br>
now we &quot;ae&quot; everything. (this was about last year.)<br>
(King,Qween of Chardok, Temple of Fear, 2nd Island of sky are just some examples.)<br>
<br>
Heres some 'tips' that i've found<br>
For the chanters out there:<br>
-Load as many stuns so that you dont have any downtime waiting for the stuns to refresh. <br>
If you have to &quot;wait&quot; for your stun to refresh, you are going to get hit. <br>
<br>
For the Wizards:<br>
-Load 2 PB ae's (the ones over level 50) and chain cast them as fast as possible. <br>
-Use Jyll's pulse to interrupt/stun briefly (this spell also helps to get the mobs off the chanter.)<br>
If the wizards dont chain cast PB's the chanter will get hit more. If chanters die &quot;you&quot; die.<br>
<br>
For the puller:<br>
Best way is to &quot;invs&quot; the tank have them go out and &quot;find&quot; a bunch to pull. The tank MUST pull more then 5 mobs. 8-10 seem to be a perfect number in order for the tank to be able to make it back alive.<br>
<br>
For the healer:<br>
Yes, Clerics can AE too! with a 'good' Ae group, the cleric will only have to heal the tank &quot;once&quot; per pull, he'll be FM most the time, so why not have him AE too!<br>
<br>
General Tips:<br>
-If you only have 1-2 mobs, the chanter can mez OR chain stun them until the tank can pull more.<br>
-Make sure the wizards are FM before you pull.<br>
-Runes saves lives, runes/manashields can also prevent spell interruptions.<br>
<br>
Good Places to AE:<br>
-Karnors Basement<br>
-Chardok<br>
-Seb Disco Area and chief<br>
-The Hole (careful some mobs are unstunable/Unmezable, ie. <br>
golems)<br>
-DN (the traps) (about .5 to 1 blue per trap)<br>
&quot;any outdoor area with lots of mobs&quot;<br>
BW<br>
Raptors in TD<br>
DL<br>
<br>
&quot;There is nothing like getting half a blue bubble of exp per pull.&quot;<br>
<br>
-Graffy <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.showMessage?topicID=1707.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.showMessage?topicID=1700.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=1641.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.threadControl?topicID=1641.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1641.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1641.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub16.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="druzzilro86846generaldiscussion">General Discussion<option value="druzzilro86846frm10">IRL<option value="druzzilro86846frm8">Raids<option value="druzzilro86846marketplace">Market Place<option value="druzzilro86846questsinfoandhelp">Quests, Info and help<option value="druzzilro86846frm7">Role-Players and Story-Tellers<option value="druzzilro86846frm11">The Admin Vault<option value="druzzi